Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.40,0:00:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家，卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看的時候要注意保持屋內亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家有崇拜的物件嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.40,0:00:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又帥啊～又有氣質啊～自己也想成為那樣的人啊～那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.60,0:00:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說就是蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.60,0:00:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能能夠和自己崇拜的人同台演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.40,0:00:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個好機會絕對要得到！得到！得到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多之星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的第一個主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹……幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.20,0:02:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依昂 依昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.20,0:02:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依昂啊依昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依昂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，依昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.00,0:02:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是那個和蕾拉小姐合拍電影的依昂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空不是他的崇拜者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.40,0:02:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幫我們一個忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊，不過幫什麼忙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在啊 在啊，就是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.80,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是擁有價值百萬美元微笑的，美國的大眾情人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.00,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部電影的主角一定得由蕾拉出演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.00,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我的第一部負責制作的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事我記得已經正式的拒絕過你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白，蕾拉的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇～價值百萬美元的微笑～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是因為感到壓力所以想要放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，卡洛斯，我希望你能夠說服她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.60,0:03:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.00,0:03:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到我這裏來做事是她最好的選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，請說服她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉，還是去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，那就去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就OK了？太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉已經答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼祝你拍攝順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯……等……啊？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們……去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.00,0:04:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去看我們新劇目的舞臺裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……沒有聽說過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你一個人在那自說自話，不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這……這個是有很大的原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丟人的事以後請不要再做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好，你也過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我嗎？為什麼是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.40,0:04:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，依昂也去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我也很想去啊，不過不過……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在建設階段，不過你們可以先看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，你們來遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是新作《天方夜譚》的鋼索裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮的一幕將在這個上面表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，好像挺棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過畢竟還只是走鋼索吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要表演的話，表演多少次都可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我這次的電影……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，它動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預定完成之後還有更複雜的移動軌跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是希望我的電影裏也有船吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉要定購條船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，要大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真有點難度呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.40,0:06:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個上面將表演盜賊一對一的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.80,0:06:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在正式演出時設想船是著火的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.70,0:06:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太胡鬧了，蕾拉，還是不要……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.50,0:06:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火啊火，蕾拉要加上火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點去預定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由利，我們儘快開始練習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是我演你的對手戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我對手戲的出演者需要進行試演嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.90,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，贊助商雅格尼斯先生已經指定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.40,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天方夜譚的高潮一幕由蕾拉和空合演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和……蕾拉小姐合演？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯和雅格尼斯都怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人魚公主都不能算是很成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是雅格尼斯先生說如果是蕾拉和空合演的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.40,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將出原來預算二倍的贊助費
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有自信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的話，你就自己退出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話，雅格尼斯先生也就無話可說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯，這孩子不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話，《天方夜譚》只會演砸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說都太玄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.20,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和由利會再討論一下劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅格尼斯先生會很失望的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.30,0:08:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我試試，蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你下定決心了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個新人怎麼那麼多要求呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還沒有自信……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連自信都沒有啊，哦，我的天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請測試一下我的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.10,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其測試以後再放棄，不如現在就放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中途換人只會給大家添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.00,0:08:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了結論之後請通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.40,0:08:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在搖晃的船上走鋼索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個真的很困難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連蕾拉小姐都會掉下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，你會走鋼索嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，多少會一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，快下來，不許再在上面耍雜技了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說空啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般這種情況下不會說“我想試試”的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的話肯定就自己退出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你會去試的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，可能的確太勉強了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了你改變劇本原來的計畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預算已經超支了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.30,0:09:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈，電影開場時就是火焰火焰火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一幕也是，全部都是火焰火焰火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？燃燒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.70,0:09:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會那麼在意她的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.00,0:09:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天觀眾會為了看她的表演而聚集在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於下決定了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.00,0:09:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去找個優秀的女演員做主角吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好……啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.90,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我……拍攝計畫取消了？不會吧？真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要人陪你聊聊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺我還是第一次有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為了什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為空吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她擁有你所沒有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.80,0:10:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她總是亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你……不，我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.80,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至是整個卡萊多劇團都沒有人會象她那樣亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.90,0:10:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.10,0:10:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過卡洛斯賞識她的原因，或許就是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然我明白你的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去卡萊多劇團吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.70,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……我還是應該自己退出嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.80,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了這由你自己決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這次我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯，就測試一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也參加測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能合演，就以此來判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期限是一周後吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.00,0:11:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.90,0:11:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的演技？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，燒著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.80,0:11:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的，你太過分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰過分啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你，害我做了被燒死的噩夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.50,0:12:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被壓著做的夢不應該是被火燒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是被浸在水裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，就是這感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.90,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.30,0:12:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看前面，別看下麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空素質還真不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.80,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，但是還遠遠未夠到和雷拉小姐合演的水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.90,0:12:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了，放掉橫杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始讓船稍微的搖晃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，已經……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.80,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間不夠了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.80,0:12:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的演出，你已經被整個烤了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整烤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話還差的遠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過越來越順利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是開始習慣鋼索了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美亞，阿娜，今天的課結束了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我還想練會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.50,0:13:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去克服你的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的弱點？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.00,0:14:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.20,0:14:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滅卻心頭火亦涼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬分感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是藍獅座的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果這顆星星出現的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現的話我們就叫它流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說覺得自己已經是無用之身就不要做他想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕火，不怕火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.10,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的弱點是害怕被整烤的恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要克服它，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔心掉落的時候就更應該盡情的跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.60,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道我哪里弄錯了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒那麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.90,0:14:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，那麼你就加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要到和蕾拉小姐交換的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎？設備一直在暗轉著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.20,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,練習的不順利嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本上能夠抓住感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.00,0:15:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是僅僅是只能走鋼索的程度就去參加測試……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你的演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼短的時間就能做到這樣……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐一定認同你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我總覺得還缺了點什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫥子打不開……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰幹的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己弄的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.40,0:16:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她自己覺得不可能通過蕾拉小姐的測試的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空竹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空竹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強的話練不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太累了的話去洗澡……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.10,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱的時候還是先去洗澡……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去洗澡……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，快，停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫魯，在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.00,0:16:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳得太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到交換的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就到期限了，我期待著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.90,0:17:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.20,0:17:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天啊，練習到次就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健，謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我會盡力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是還想再練一會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.80,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個當然啦，不過已經……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波力士先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.70,0:18:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是上次治我的父親的醫生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我叫凱特，你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是約會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.00,0:18:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事，我們只是從小就認識了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在等我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找波力士先生商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.30,0:18:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧凱特小姐認識位元遊樂園管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們全家都是你的人魚公主的崇拜者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，實地練習啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.00,0:18:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.40,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.70,0:18:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我們要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.10,0:19:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，萬分……感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個星期就能做到這樣，夠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.60,0:19:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一跳還是太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不壓低點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.20,0:19:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那樣才象空的作風啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.60,0:19:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擔心掉落的時候就更應該盡情的跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能掉下去也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.50,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太精彩了，不愧是蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，接下去輪到空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.00,0:20:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面就是最後一跳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.90,0:20:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有聽天由命試一試！試！試！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.60,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳得太高了，落足點會錯過鋼索的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.80,0:21:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表演的比我預期的還要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉，怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這回沒話說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，雅格尼斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.60,0:21:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和空將會表演出什麼樣的劇目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.70,0:21:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確，你有我所沒有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.10,0:22:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要和我同台演出，你要有相當的思想準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.80,0:22:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.60,0:22:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照
